Intro:
    using Warp Perspective Transformation to get the original image
    (straighten the image)
Requirement:
    Ubuntu      16.04 LTS
    opencv      3.1.0
    gcc         5.4.0
Compile:
    g++ -o t test.cpp -I /usr/local/include/opencv2/ -L /usr/lib/ -lopencv_core -lopencv_highgui -lopencv_imgproc -lopencv_imgcodecs  -lopencv_highgui
    


